https://www.codetutorial.io/loopback-and-angularjs-first-tutorial/

create new model to existing project command : "slc loopback:model" after this run command lb-ng server/server.js client/js/lb-services.js
for angular support

methods: https://loopback.io/doc/en/lb2/AngularJS-JavaScript-SDK.html

if u want to change model that is already created edit common/models/model_name.json file in root directory of application

